It is the largest stadium in Syria , and is currently used mostly for football matches . It serves as a home ground of Al - Ittihad . The stadium was opened in 2007 and holds 75,000 spectators . Al - Ittihad played a friendly match against Fenerbah√ße SK of Turkey on 3 April 2007 for the opening of the stadium which ended in a 2 - 2 draw . It is considered one of the worlds cleanest and most well - kept stadiums in the world . The president himself has attended the opening of the stadium . 